{"segment_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-001", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i", "source_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 泰誓上 [1]", "text_original": "惟十有三年，春，大會于孟津。王曰：「嗟我友邦冢君，越我御事庶士，明聽誓。", "text_normalized": "惟十有三年，春，大會于孟津。王曰：「嗟我友邦冢君，越我御事庶士，明聽誓。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-002", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i", "source_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 泰誓上 [2]", "text_original": "惟天地，萬物父母；惟人，萬物之靈。亶聰明，作元後，元後作民父母。今商王受，弗敬上天，降災下民，沈緬冒色，敢行暴虐。罪人以族，官人以世。惟宮室、臺榭、陂池、侈服，以殘害于爾萬姓。焚炙忠良，刳剔孕婦。", "text_normalized": "惟天地，萬物父母；惟人，萬物之靈。亶聰明，作元後，元後作民父母。今商王受，弗敬上天，降災下民，沈緬冒色，敢行暴虐。罪人以族，官人以世。惟宮室、臺榭、陂池、侈服，以殘害于爾萬姓。焚炙忠良，刳剔孕婦。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-003", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i", "source_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 泰誓上 [3]", "text_original": "「皇天震怒，命我文考，肅將天威，大勛未集。", "text_normalized": "「皇天震怒，命我文考，肅將天威，大勛未集。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-004", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i", "source_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 泰誓上 [4]", "text_original": "肆予小子發，以爾友邦冢君，觀政于商，惟受罔有悛心，乃夷居，弗事上帝神祗，遺厥先宗廟弗祀。犧牲粢盛，既于兇盜。乃曰：『吾有民有命，罔懲其侮。』", "text_normalized": "肆予小子發，以爾友邦冢君，觀政于商，惟受罔有悛心，乃夷居，弗事上帝神祗，遺厥先宗廟弗祀。犧牲粢盛，既于兇盜。乃曰：『吾有民有命，罔懲其侮。』", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-005", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i", "source_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 泰誓上 [5]", "text_original": "天佑下民，作之君、作之師。惟其克相上帝，寵綏四方。有罪無罪，予曷敢有越厥志？", "text_normalized": "天佑下民，作之君、作之師。惟其克相上帝，寵綏四方。有罪無罪，予曷敢有越厥志？", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-006", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i", "source_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 泰誓上 [6]", "text_original": "同力度德，同德度義，受有臣億萬，惟億萬心。予有臣三千，惟一心。商罪貫盈，天命誅之，予弗順天，厥罪惟鈞。", "text_normalized": "同力度德，同德度義，受有臣億萬，惟億萬心。予有臣三千，惟一心。商罪貫盈，天命誅之，予弗順天，厥罪惟鈞。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-007", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i", "source_id": "shangshu-029-zhou-shu-great-declaration-i__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 泰誓上 [7]", "text_original": "予小子夙夜祗懼，受命文考，類于上帝，宜于冢土，以爾有眾，厎天之罰。天矜于民，民之所欲，天必從之。爾尚弼予一人，永清四海。時哉！弗可失。」", "text_normalized": "予小子夙夜祗懼，受命文考，類于上帝，宜于冢土，以爾有眾，厎天之罰。天矜于民，民之所欲，天必從之。爾尚弼予一人，永清四海。時哉！弗可失。」", "notes": ""}
